{
  "name": "Covering Stance",
  "type": "feat",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Just your presence on the field of battle protects nearby allies from possible harm. While you are in this stance, choose one ally adjacent to you at the end of your turn to gain the benefits of lesser cover until the start of your next turn. That ally loses this benefit if they move so that they are no longer adjacent to you. If you Intercept a Strike that would harm that ally while they are benefiting from your lesser cover, that ally can Step as a free action.</p>"
